@startuml C3_Manage_Docks_Process_View
title C3 – Manage Docks (Process View / System Sequence Diagram)
hide footbox

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "DocksController\n(API Layer)" as Controller
participant "DockMapper\n(Conversão DTO ↔ Entidade)" as Mapper
participant "PortContext\n(Entity Framework Core)" as Context
database "Database System\n(SQL / InMemory)" as DB

Officer -> Controller : POST /api/Docks (CreateDockDTO)
Controller -> Mapper : Converte DTO para Entidade Dock
Mapper --> Controller : Retorna Entidade Dock
Controller -> Context : Adiciona Dock e chama SaveChanges()
Context -> DB : INSERT INTO Docks (...)
DB --> Context : Confirma inserção
Controller --> Officer : HTTP 201 Created (DockDTO)

@enduml

